  "segments": [
    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 135.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第135课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "The Latest Report.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "最新消息。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "Listen to the tape, then answer this question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答这个问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Is Karen Marsh going to retire, do you think?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "你认为卡伦·马什会退休吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "Are you really going to retire, Miss Marsh?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "马什小姐，您真的准备退休吗？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "I may.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "有可能。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "I can't make up my mind.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我还拿不定主意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "I will have to ask my future husband.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我得问问我未来的丈夫。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "He won't let me make another film.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他不会让我再拍电影了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "Your future husband, Miss Marsh?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "您未来的丈夫，马什小姐？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "Yes.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "是的。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "Let me introduce him to you.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "让我把他介绍给你们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "His name is Carlos.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他叫卡洛斯。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s014",
      "text": "We're going to get married next week.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "我们下周就要结婚了。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s015",
      "text": "Look, Liz.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "看，莉兹。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s016",
      "text": "Here's another report about Karen Marsh.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这里又有一篇关于卡伦·马什的报道。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s017",
      "text": "Listen.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听着。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s018",
      "text": "Karen Marsh.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "卡伦·马什。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s019",
      "text": "The Latest.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "最新消息。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s020",
      "text": "At her London hotel today, Miss Marsh told reporters she might retire.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "今天，马什小姐在她下榻的伦敦酒店告诉记者，她可能会退休。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s021",
      "text": "She said she couldn't make up her mind.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她说她还拿不定主意。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s022",
      "text": "She said she would have to ask her future husband.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她说她得问问她未来的丈夫。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s023",
      "text": "She said her future husband would not let her make another film.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "她说她未来的丈夫不会让她再拍电影。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s024",
      "text": "Then she introduced us to Carlos and told us they would get married next week.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "随后她把卡洛斯介绍给我们，并告诉我们他们将在下周结婚。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s025",
      "text": "That sensational news, isn't it, Kate?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "这可是条轰动性的新闻，对吧，凯特？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s026",
      "text": "It certainly is.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "的确是。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s027",
      "text": "He'll be her sixth husband.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他将是她的第六任丈夫。"
      }
    }
  ],
